org.greencheek.processio.service.scheduler
Class ScheduledExecutorServiceProcessIOScheduler

java.lang.Object
  org.greencheek.processio.service.scheduler.ScheduledExecutorServiceProcessIOScheduler
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProcessIOScheduler
public class ScheduledExecutorServiceProcessIOScheduler
extends Object
implements ProcessIOScheduler

Uses a single threaded executor service the contains a runnable task that simply:

  • calls ProcessIOReader.getCurrentProcessIO()
  • asks for the resulting CurrentProcessIO to be persisted by the implementation of ProcessIOUsagePersistence
  • The CurrentProcessIO is only requested to be persisted if is not the ProcessIOReader.NON_READABLE_PROCESS_IO instance
